Extract from this graph:
1. Title
2. X-axis label
3. Y-axis label
4. Legend (if present)
5. ALL data values
Required JSON format:
{
    "title": str or null,
    "x_label": str or null,
    "y_label": str or null,
    "legend": ["serie1", "serie2"] or null,
    "data": [{"x": x1, "y": y1}, {"x": x2, "y": y2}, {"x": x3, "y": y3}, ...]
}
Return ONLY the JSON object, nothing else.
